
<title>Bloccit</title>

<style type="text/css">
h2{
    margin: 0;     
    color: #fff;
    padding-top: 90px;
    font-size: 64px;
    font-family: "trebuchet ms", sans-serif;    
}
.item{
    background: #333;    
    text-align: center;
    height: 300px !important;
}
.carousel{
    margin-top: 20px;
}
.bs-example{
  margin: 20px;
}
</style>

<body>
<div class="bs-example">
    <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-interval="3000" data-ride="carousel">
      
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        </ol>   
       
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="active item">
                <h2>Bloccit</h2>
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                  <h3>A Bloc project</h3>
                  <p>Created by Reinaldo L Sanchez.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <h2>Sign Up Now for Access!</h2>
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                  <h3>All accounts are free</h3>
                  <p>Click those buttons up there!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <h2>Interactive Site</h2>
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                  <h3>Contribute content and vote up or down on whether it's any good.</h3>
                  <p>Create fun topics or dumb ones.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-control left" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left"></span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control right" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="next">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>
        </a>
       </div>
</div>
<p>
<%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %> or 
<%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %> today!

 <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4">
          <h3>Solves world hunger</h3>
          <p>Bloccit will next day deliver food to the hungry, if we get the donations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4">
          <h3>Post things important to you by you</h3>
          <p>We challenge you to find a better way to waste life than on this site!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4">
          <h3>Better looks guaranteed.</h3>
          <p>AniBloccit will make you look better and the free black makeup under your eyes never ends!</p>
        </div>
